    {
      "section_id": "para_32",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An  Act  to  provide  the  restructured  local  authorities  with  grants \nthrough the State Governments for the specific purpose of assisting \nthe  local  authorities  to maintain  themselves.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_33",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[1  January  1978]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_34",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "WHEREAS by Clause (3) of Article 109 of the Federal Constitution \nit is provided that Parliament may by law make grants for specific \npurposes to any of the States on such terms and conditions as may \nbe  provided  by  such  law;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_35",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "NOW THEREFORE BE IT ENACTED by the Seri Paduka Baginda \nYang di-Pertuan Agong with the advice and consent of the Dewan \nNegara  and  Dewan  Rakyat  in  Parliament  assembled,  and  by  the \nauthority  of  the  same, as  follows:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_36",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Short  title  and  commencement",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_37",
      "heading": "1.    This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  State  Grants  (Maintenance  of \nLocal Authorities)  Act  1981  and  shall  be  deemed  to  have  come \ninto  force  on  1  January  1978.",
      "content": "1.    This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  State  Grants  (Maintenance  of \nLocal Authorities)  Act  1981  and  shall  be  deemed  to  have  come \ninto  force  on  1  January  1978.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_38",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Grant  to  any  State  by  the  Federation",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_39",
      "heading": "2.    (1)    The  Federation  may  from  time  to  time  make  a  grant  to \nanyState for  the  maintenance of  local  authorities  in  that  State.",
      "content": "2.    (1)    The  Federation  may  from  time  to  time  make  a  grant  to \nanyState for  the  maintenance of  local  authorities  in  that  State.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_40",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)    The  amount  of  the  grant  made  under  subsection  (1)  shall \nbe determined  by  the  Minister  responsible  for  local  government \nafter consultation  with  the  Minister  of  Finance.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_41",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6                                     Laws of Malaysia                             ACT 245",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_42",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Federation  may  impose  terms  and  conditions",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_43",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3.    The  Federation,  in  making  such  grant,  may  impose  terms  and \nconditions  to  be  observed  by  the  State  including  a  condition  that \nthe  grant  is  to  be  spent  by  the  local  authorities  for  a  specific \npurpose.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
